{"tid":1702760,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"墮落港","createTime":"2019-11-10T01:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:10:05.000Z","uid":202865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0d0dd0c06594ae893777465c34af823edbe0f9","tid":1702760,"uid":202865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"他，<br />\n終究還是掉了下來。<br />\n<br />\n那夜凌晨，<br />\n月色朦朧。<br />\n<br />\n地面煙霧瀰漫，<br />\n黃光與黑影的交疊隱約可見。<br />\n<br />\n燈亮了，<br />\n映照著男孩的側臉。<br />\n他正低著頭，<br />\n陷入沉思。<br />\n<br />\n蒙面殺手上前，<br />\n齜牙咧嘴一笑。<br />\n突然從後摟住了男孩，<br />\n再用手捂著了他的口鼻，<br />\n閉住了他的氣道。<br />\n<br />\n男孩顏面發青，<br />\n呼吸開始變得困難；<br />\n原本強而有力的心跳亦慢慢變得微弱。<br />\n<br />\n他漸漸失去掙扎的能力⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n殺手猛力一推。<br />\n<br />\n「呯！」<br />\n男孩躺臥在地上，<br />\n鮮血從他的頭顱潺潺而出，<br />\n隨即染紅了千絲萬縷。<br />\n<br />\n血液在黑夜中閃著寒光，<br />\n罌粟之海回歸寂靜。"},{"pid":"1e69f808253c8b4baf9eff34d4b6a67b471e5b91","tid":1702760,"uid":202865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"我對著鏡子問：<br />\n「下一個會是誰？」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n習慣墮落；<br />\n對罌栗甘之如飴；<br />\n慶幸自己不是受害人，<br />\n乃一種社會病態。<br />\n<br />\n*註：罌栗學名為 papaver somniferum，而當中的 somniferum具有催眠之意。同時罌栗的提取物亦是多種麻醉藥的原材料。"},{"pid":"3b69f81e219dff113a9ac477341c0510808d97ce","tid":1702760,"uid":202865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYbhh56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYbhh56.jpg&h=caa2ac97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nHiO9cN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnHiO9cN.png&h=b5bf5b55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOyb6Zt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOyb6Zt.png&h=76c74a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我無嘢講。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}